{# ======================================
This template is the first stage in handling the display of multiple entries on a single page.

It ensures that differing content models (currently just entries or categores) are routed to
templates that can handle the supplied data correctly. It also allows for a flexible override
system to be used so more unique or complex templates can be used for specific Category Groups
or Entry Sections/Channels
========================================= #}

{% set defaultListingType = category is defined ? 'entriesByCategory' : 'entries' %}
{% set override = category is defined ? category.group.handle : entry.section.handle %}

{% include [
	'_listing/' ~ override,
	'_listing/handlers/' ~ defaultListingType,
] %}